An implementation of the model object 'L2 Interface'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Auto Negotiation
  • Broadcast
  • Duplex
  • Encapsulation
  • Hw Address
  • Index
  • L2 Interface Name
  • Loopback
  • Mtu
  • Private
  • Promiscuous
  • Speed
